#: ../../../admin-guide/media/vivid.rst:4
msgid "The Virtual Video Test Driver (vivid)"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../admin-guide/media/vivid.rst:6
msgid ""
"This driver emulates video4linux hardware of various types: video capture, "
"video output, vbi capture and output, metadata capture and output, radio "
"receivers and transmitters, touch capture and a software defined radio "
"receiver. In addition a simple framebuffer device is available for testing "
"capture and output overlays."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../admin-guide/media/vivid.rst:11
msgid ""
"Up to 64 vivid instances can be created, each with up to 16 inputs and 16 "
"outputs."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../admin-guide/media/vivid.rst:13
msgid ""
"Each input can be a webcam, TV capture device, S-Video capture device or an "
"HDMI capture device. Each output can be an S-Video output device or an HDMI "
"output device."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../admin-guide/media/vivid.rst:17
msgid ""
"These inputs and outputs act exactly as a real hardware device would behave. "
"This allows you to use this driver as a test input for application "
"development, since you can test the various features without requiring "
"special hardware."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../admin-guide/media/vivid.rst:21
msgid "This document describes the features implemented by this driver:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../admin-guide/media/vivid.rst:23
msgid "Support for read()/write(), MMAP, USERPTR and DMABUF streaming I/O."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../admin-guide/media/vivid.rst:24
msgid "A large list of test patterns and variations thereof"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../admin-guide/media/vivid.rst:25
msgid "Working brightness, contrast, saturation and hue controls"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../admin-guide/media/vivid.rst:26
msgid "Support for the alpha color component"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../admin-guide/media/vivid.rst:27
msgid "Full colorspace support, including limited/full RGB range"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../admin-guide/media/vivid.rst:28
msgid "All possible control types are present"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../admin-guide/media/vivid.rst:29
msgid "Support for various pixel aspect ratios and video aspect ratios"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../admin-guide/media/vivid.rst:30
msgid "Error injection to test what happens if errors occur"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../admin-guide/media/vivid.rst:31
msgid ""
"Supports crop/compose/scale in any combination for both input and output"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../admin-guide/media/vivid.rst:32
msgid "Can emulate up to 4K resolutions"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../admin-guide/media/vivid.rst:33
msgid "All Field settings are supported for testing interlaced capturing"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../admin-guide/media/vivid.rst:34
msgid ""
"Supports all standard YUV and RGB formats, including two multiplanar YUV "
"formats"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../admin-guide/media/vivid.rst:35
msgid "Raw and Sliced VBI capture and output support"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../admin-guide/media/vivid.rst:36
msgid "Radio receiver and transmitter support, including RDS support"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../admin-guide/media/vivid.rst:37
msgid "Software defined radio (SDR) support"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../admin-guide/media/vivid.rst:38
msgid "Capture and output overlay support"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../admin-guide/media/vivid.rst:39
msgid "Metadata capture and output support"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../admin-guide/media/vivid.rst:40
msgid "Touch capture support"
msgstr ""

