msgstr ""

#: ../../../admin-guide/media/vivid.rst:253
msgid ""
"Enable scaling support. Scaling can scale the incoming buffer. The scaler of "
"the vivid driver can enlarge up or down to four times the original size. The "
"scaler is very simple and low-quality. Simplicity and speed were key, not "
"quality."
msgstr ""

