"including a control like 'Disconnect' which emulates a USB disconnect, "
"making the device inaccessible and so all tests that v4l2-compliance is "
"doing will fail afterwards."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../admin-guide/media/vivid.rst:282
msgid ""
"There may be other situations as well where you want to disable the error "
"injection support of vivid. When this option is set, then the controls that "
"select crop, compose and scale behavior are also removed. Unless overridden "
"by ccs_cap_mode and/or ccs_out_mode the will default to enabling crop, "
